sequenceDiagram
    participant C as MCP Client (Agent)
    participant S as TigerMCP Server (FastMCP)
    participant QA as QuoteApi
    participant TA as TradeApi
    participant QS as Quote Service
    participant TS as Trade Service

    C->>S: call_tool(get_realtime_quote, params)
    S->>QA: validate -> QuoteClient
    QA->>QS: HTTP/SDK request
    QS-->>QA: DataFrame / JSON
    QA-->>S: list(dict)
    S-->>C: JSON response

    C->>S: call_tool(place_order, params)
    S->>TA: _prepare_order -> TradeClient
    TA->>TS: place_order API
    TS-->>TA: order id / result
    TA-->>S: structured result
    S-->>C: JSON response
